---
title: Group Membership
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NonMember

    NonMember --> Invited: receive invitation
    Invited --> Member: accept invitation
    Invited --> NonMember: decline invitation
    Invited --> NonMember: invitation revoked

    Member --> NonMember: removed from group
    Member --> [*]: group deleted
    NonMember --> [*]: user deleted

    state Member {
        [*] --> Active
        Active --> HasClaims: claims item via this group
        HasClaims --> Active: unclaims all
        HasClaims --> Active: claims released
    }

    note right of Invited
        Notification sent
        Can accept or decline
    end note

    note right of Member
        Can see items tagged with group
        Can claim those items
        Can invite others
    end note

    note left of HasClaims
        On leave: claims released
        On group delete: claims released
        Notified of releases
    end note
